Homepage


                    
                        About
                    
                










                        MEET SIZMEK
                    

Create impressions that inspire and gain the power to connect.














Impressions That Inspire

Sizmek provides you with powerful, integrated solutions so your creative and data work together in all new ways, optimizing campaigns across all media.



    Contact a Pro to Learn More












What makes Sizmek different?
We believe that in the digital world, creating impressions that inspire is vital to building meaningful, long-lasting relationships with your customers. Sizmek provides you with powerful, integrated solutions so your creative and data work together in all new ways, optimizing campaigns across all media. We believe that when your messages resonate, your impact amplifies, and your business reaches new heights. 
Sizmek’s particular combination of technology, intelligence, creative solutions, and strategic service empowers you to create advertising experiences that cultivate deeper relationships and drive campaign performance around the world. Engage your audiences in unique ways around their interests while distinguishing yourself from the many voices crowding every other moment of their day—this is how you create impressions that inspire. With Sizmek, you gain the insight, knowledge, and ability to do this, to serve the right ads to the right people at exactly the right time. 
Where audience meets advertising—here is where Sizmek excels. From a range of easy-to-use creative tools to holistic analysis to dynamic targeting that puts the most relevant creative in front of each viewer, we bring creativity and data together so you can deliver truly inspiring ad experiences. This applies as much to programmatic buying as it does to premium and direct. You tell the engaging, connected story you want, no matter how or where you’re buying. 
As you build connection, you also discover further insights about your audience. It’s more important than ever to be able to use those insights to continue to optimize your campaign delivery across all channels and media—mobile, display, rich media, video, and so on. We make that easy. Sizmek’s data platform powers your campaigns with sophisticated targeting, data collection, attribution, and decisioning tools. You keep your brand safe, protect against fraud, and verify your delivery, all in real-time, and across media, devices, and touchpoints. No silos, no walled gardens—receive comprehensive, transparent data systematically organized how you want and need it. We provide you with a holistic understanding of what is happening with your campaign and your brand, so you can optimize across the board. 
The Sizmek experience allows you to be unfettered, unbounded as you continue on the journey to know and connect to your audience more deeply than ever before. Sizmek helps you resonate globally, connecting more than 20,000 advertisers and 3,600 agencies to audiences in 70 countries, seamlessly serving over 2.3 trillion impressions each year. With Sizmek, you create impressions that inspire and you gain the power to connect with your audiences in ways you never thought possible. 












Sizmek Advertising Suite, Game-Changing Campaign Performance

Sizmek Advertising Suite helps differentiate your brand from the competition, drive performance, and personalize experiences across your strategy.



    Learn More















Get to Know Our Team

Our team is made up of leaders in the field dedicated to keeping you on the cutting edge of ad tech.



    Learn About Our Team













